snippet.title: Royal Rewind: Meghan Markle's Friends Speak Out Amid 'Distressing And Upsetting’ ‘Bullying’ Claims
snippet.description:
This week on Royal Rewind, Meghan Markle's close friends are coming to her defence, saying that the "bullying" claims made by former royal aides are both "distressing and upsetting" and couldn't be further from the truth. Plus, get the latest health update on Prince Philip.
